description:
Plot Summary

This issue of My Greatest Adventure contains the following three stories:

  • I Stalked the Camouflage Creatures!
  • We Battled the Microscopic Menace!
  • We Wore the Forbidden Masks!

It also features the following comic strip:

  • Professor Eureka

I Stalked the Camouflage Creatures

When Dr.Munston learns that all of his equipment has been stolen he contacts the U.S. Government for help. In response Special Agent Blake is assigned to the case. Together Blake and Dr.Munston discover a strange new batch of creatures that can disguise themselves as normal objects, but why are they here and what do they plan on doing with Munston's equipment?

We Battled the Microscopic Menace

Marcus Drake and Professor Elliot Saunders are on the brink of a new discover for the science of micro-chemistry; however, when a strange foreign bacteria dubbed Micro-X arrives things take a turn for the worse. Now an alien threat has been unleashed on the city and only Marcus and Elliot have the knowledge to stop it.

We Wore the Forbidden Masks

While scouting out a new location for Vacation Magazine, Martin comes across a strange salesmen who offers him three mysterious masks. Martin gifts two of the masks to his fellow friends, believing the masks to be ordinary masks. When Martin and his friends wear the masks all chaos breaks loose as the power of the Forbidden Masks is unleashed!

Professor Eureka

The Professor attempts retirement for the first time!
name: We Wore the Forbidden Masks

Plot Summary

This issue of My Greatest Adventure contains the following three stories:

  • I Tracked the Forbidden Powers!
  • I Reported the Impossible Space Scoops!
  • We Unleashed the Thermo-Men of Silent Valley!

It also contains the following comic strips:

  • The Magic Genie
  • Doctor Rocket

I Tracked the Forbidden Powers

Mr. Jamison of the Adventurer's Club is hired by a businessman named Roland Petry. His mission is to obtain the magical object known as the Sorcerers Belt; an artifact of great power that grants its wearer the abilities of super strength, super speed and invulnerability. With the aid of his friend, Jaun, Mr. Jamison embarks on the adventure of a lifetime.

I Reported the Impossible Space Scoops

Stu Crane is one of the galaxies top space reporters; gathering news and scoops from Mercury to Pluto; however, after a strange series of phony stories it seems that someone or something is out to get him. Is Stu the subject of a bigger plan or is he just going crazy?

We Unleashed the Thermo-Men of Silent Valley

The location of Silent Valley was chosen for a variety of field tests for Professor Mark Tanner's lab tested atomic transmuter and materializer known as Atam. As it's being tested it detects a strange anomaly which is discovered to be the Thermo-Men of Silent Valley!

The Magic Genie

The Magic Genie is called upon to do a series of mundane favors from those who find the lamp. Will he ever escape these boring tasks?

Doctor Rocket

Doctor Rocket prepares his arsenal of space weaponry should he and his assistant get attacked.
name: We Unleashed the Thermo-Men of Silent Valley

description:
Menace of the Super-Gorilla

Who was piloting the fantastic craft that darted so fast around the city it could not be seen? Only the Flash--by matching the craft's speed--could bring it into his field of vision--thereby revealing a tantalizing puzzle that extended thousands of miles across the world to an even greater suprise--and greater danger! in the "Menace of the Super-Gorilla!"

Trivia: this is the first appearances of Gorilla Grodd and Solovar

The Pied Piper of Peril!

He burst onto the city like a tornado--a tornado of incredible sound! Who was he? Where did he gain his amazing powers? None knew...and none could handle the amazing criminal until the Flash--Fastest Man Alive--catapulted onto the scene and came to grips with "The Pied Piper of Peril!"

Trivia: This is the first appearance of the Pied Piper
name: Menace of the Super-Gorilla / The Pied Piper of Peril!

Plot Summary

This issue of My Greatest Adventure contains the following three stories:

  • We Cruised into the Supernatural!
  • I Battled the Doom from the Deep!
  • We Were Trapped as Human Puppets!

It also features the following comic strip:

  • Doctor Rocket

We Cruised into the Supernatural

A unique society of the worlds wealthiest men sought out adventures known by no other. When they meet a magical man known as Maki they laugh off his tales and bash his mysticism; however, after they find themselves at the Port of the Supernatural they realize that they're in for more than they bargained for!

I Battled the Doom from the Deep

Two seafaring Captains are caught off guard when attacked by a strange green goop floating through the ocean. Before long the green mass becomes larger and larger and the two must do all they can to battle the doom from the deep!

We Were Trapped as Human Puppets

A group of four travelers are blown off course after their fishing boat encounters a large storm. When they finally arrive on land they come face to face with a creature from another dimension, turning the four travelers into human puppets. Now they must do everything it commands, including building a device that might doom the Earth!

Doctor Rocket

Doctor Rocket and his assistant test out the most powerful rocket ship they've ever made!
name: We Were Trapped As Human Puppets
